<br>
I was approached by someone from your LARP troupe that informed me of this game's occurance.<br>
<br>
I figured the least I could do was to take a gander and see what there was to see.<br>
<br>
My name is Dan, friends call me Logan. Long story..<br>
<br>
Regardless, I just wanted to send a greeting to you all. Glad to see a new group in existance. I have been gaming in the Bay Area for about 7 - 8 years now with the same crew and am always looking for new opportunites!<br>
<br>
