sorry but I think it is funny.  at least the anthro students played along with us.<br>
<br>
All games are basically the same.  The ST/GM is either great or doing their best (even the wankers try their best).  The players consist of everything from dreamy perfect theater type folks, to well meaning escapists, to clueless twerps, to cheating dingbats who everyone is aware of and works around, some are just there to play, some are looking for their only social outlet, some have no other life.  The game either has almost too few players to not be a &quot;salon game&quot; or almost too many to track on open streets.<br>
Some nites the game rocks, some nites the game sucks.<br>
<br>
I don't mean any disrespect to anyone, and coming to check things out is always ok.  But jeez, it's a *game*.<br>
<br>
For basic questions, there are a set of links &lt;----- over there somewhere.  Lots of silly pics and some media coverage (more observers, tho the media always misses the point), game history (tho continuity is never perfect, impossible with a game that has run as long as this one has).  There are some *great* OOG literary posts, backgrounds, interactions, speculations.<br>
<br>
I hope the anthro/soc students get us a copy of their study.  I'd love to see what they thought.<br>
<br>
Again, breathe, I'm not flaming, just laughing.<br>
It takes all kinds, and we have some of each. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#FFFFFF><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub98.ezboard.com/bscbnforum58570.showUserPublicProfile?gid=vicious@scbnforum58570>Vicious</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Member</span><br>  Posts: 22<br> <font color=#FF9300>(5/29/03 11:24 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fscbnforum58570frm16.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=48.topic&index=10>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Best. Summary. Ever.</span><hr size=1> See subject line. I don't think there's a better way to put it. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub98.ezboard.com/fscbnforum58570frm16.showPrevMessage?topicID=48.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub98.ezboard.com/fscbnforum58570frm16.showNextMessage?topicID=48.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fscbnforum58570frm16.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=48.topic&index=10><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/prefabs/ez/addreply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"><a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fscbnforum58570frm16.threadControl?topicID=48.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/posticons/techops.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fscbnforum58570frm16.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=48.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/subscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to receive email notification of replies"> Click to receive email notification of replies</a> <br>  <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fscbnforum58570frm16.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=48.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/